{
  "info": {
    "name": "Almacenes INIAF - API",
    "description": "Coleccion de la API del Sistema de Almacenes.\n\nBASE: http://localhost:3000/api/v1\n\nUSO RAPIDO:\n1. Corre el backend (pnpm start:dev) y el seed (pnpm prisma db seed).\n2. Ejecuta 'Auth > Login' con el usuario admin/admin123. El accessToken y refreshToken se guardan solos en las variables de la coleccion (script en la pestana Tests del request).\n3. El resto de requests ya mandan 'Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}' heredado a nivel de coleccion.\n\nVariables editables en la pestana 'Variables' de la coleccion.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1" },
    { "key": "usuario", "value": "admin" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "admin123" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"usuario\": \"{{usuario}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "  console.log('Tokens guardados. Rol:', res.user && res.user.rol);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('login 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "refresh"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (perfil)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "me"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Usuarios",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["usuarios"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "rol", "value": "solicitador", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "unidadId", "value": "1", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "almacenId", "value": "1", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Nuevo Solicitador\",\n  \"usuario\": \"solic_test\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"rol\": \"solicitador\",\n  \"unidadId\": 1,\n  \"almacenId\": 1\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios", "1"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Nombre Editado\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (baja logica)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["usuarios", "1"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Unidades",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["unidades"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["unidades", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["unidades"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Unidad de Prueba\",\n  \"sigla\": \"UP-TEST\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["unidades", "1"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Unidad Editada\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/unidades/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["unidades", "1"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Almacenes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["almacenes"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["almacenes", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["almacenes"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Almacen de Prueba\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["almacenes", "1"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Almacen Editado\",\n  \"activo\": true\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (baja logica)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/almacenes/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["almacenes", "1"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Partidas",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar plano (paginado + filtros)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["partidas"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "39700", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "activo", "value": "true", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "seleccionable", "value": "true", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "nivel", "value": "1", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "padreId", "value": "1", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Arbol jerarquico",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas/arbol",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["partidas", "arbol"],
              "query": [{ "key": "soloActivas", "value": "true", "disabled": true }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas/1", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["partidas", "1"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Activar (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas/1/activar", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["partidas", "1", "activar"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Desactivar (solo super_admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/partidas/1/desactivar", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["partidas", "1", "desactivar"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
